To use Tweet Me Tunes:

(1) Sign in to Twitter.
(2) Follow @tweetmetunes.
(3) Go to http://tinyurl.com/tweetmetunes. Once @tweetmetunes is following you back, enter the name of an artist (and optionally a track) in the search box and click "Tweet me tunes!"
(4) Click the "Tweet" button.
(5) You will receive a recommendation as an @reply.

You don't need to (nor will you be able to) execute the bot yourself.